DESCRIPTION:<p>This year\, we celebrate 20 years since the first PROljetni
  Jam in Zagreb\, which was held back in 2005. And its 21 years since the b
 eginning of Parkour in Croatia. The number 21 holds special significance i
 n the Parkour world\, so we decided to mark this occasion in a special way
 !&nbsp\;</p></br>\n<p>PROljetni Jam is one of\, if not the oldest regularl
 y held events in the Parkour world. To make this year even more special\, 
 we are bringing a guest who is one of\, if not the oldest founder of the d
 iscipline\, and he will share his experience with us. Over the course of t
 wo days\, you will have the opportunity to train and talk with him in an o
 riginal way—without official workshops or lectures.&nbsp\;</p></br>\n<p>
 📍 Official start of the gathering:&nbsp\;</p>\n<p>➡ Saturday\, May 17
 \, 2025\, at 11:00 AM at Bundek&nbsp\;</p>\n<p>➡ Sunday\, May 18\, 2025\
 , at 12:00 PM at Ksaver</p></br>\n<p>If you're coming from outside Zagreb 
 and need accommodation\, please contact us as soon as possible via message
  here or on the event’s official Instagram page. See you at another unfo
 rgettable PROljetni Jam!</p></br>\n<p>Price: free</p>\n<p>Food: not includ
 ed</p>\n<p>Accomodation: contact them</p>
LOCATION:Bundek\, 10000\, Novi Zagreb - istok\, Zagreb\, Croatia
ORGANIZER;CN="Parkour HR";PHONE=;WEBSITE="https://fb.me/e/8e09y4QGj":MAILT
 O:emanueldolo@gmail.com
